texts.text: >At the town near Ueno Park...

*Pant*
My friends... The king...

No... Please...
Don't go without me...
>--X years ago--
>Shortly before the world was devastated by ICBMs.
>A group of Pixies are flying around their forest...
Everything's normal on this front.
Hmm, I don't see anything unusual.
Maybe King Oberon made a mistake?
Just stay alert okay? Our orders are to patrol the forest...
But this is no fun! I don't wanna do it!

I don't want to either, but...
Wait!
There, do you hear it? Sounds like something big is moving through the forest...
You're joking right? There's nothing wrong here.
Nothing at al... Whoa!!
>The ground shakes and starts to crack open...!
What's happening?! No earthquake is like this!
The trees! They're falling! By the dozens!
I guess it's safe to say this is an emergency right?!
Then we have to report back to King Oberon!
C'mon, let's head back!
Yes, let's hurry... Whoa?!

What the...?!
It's pulling me in...!!
>One of the Pixies is being pulled into the fissure on the ground!
No! Wait up everyone! Help!
>The Pixie screams out loud with hands outstretched, but her voice is drowned out by the sound of falling trees.

Wait...!
*Scream*
*Moan*
W-What happened...? I...
I was sucked into that weird crack and...
Where am I? This looks like Faerie Forest but...
Something feels off...
>*Rustling*
Eek! W-What was that?!
Oh, a stranger. A Pixie maybe...? Nah, too different.
You don't look like a High Pixie either... What are you?
H-Huh? W-What are you talking about? I'm a Pixie.
No you're not. Pixies are supposed to look like us!
There's not a Pixie that looks like you in the entire forest.
What?! Then my friends...
You okay? You face just went pale.
I have to get to King Oberon...
Oh, you're looking for King Oberon? I can take you there, just follow me!
Lord Oberonnnn.
What is it, Pixie?
Someone wants to see you, your majesty.
You're King Oberon?
Yes. I am Oberon, king of Faerie kind!
I have been king for many centuries now, a well respected demon indeed.
No... You're not the King Oberon I know.
B-But wait, there should only be one King Oberon...
This must be some kind of mistake right?
Excuse me?! Stop being rude to King Oberon!
B-But!
Hmmm. You there, the odd looking Pixie.
There's something intriguing about your story. Tell it to me in full.
I see...
Guessing from what you told me, it may be that you are a demon from another world.
Huh? What... do you mean?
You are from a world similar to this one, that exists in a totally different dimension. Other worlds outside our own do exist.
Usually these worlds exist parallel to each other, never crossing paths...
But right now our world is going through a world changing event... It wouldn't be out of the realm of possibility
that it has brought about the occurrence of events that normally should not happen.
No...
O what a sad little thing you are, child.
The migration between worlds is not something that can be done at will.
Finding a way back would not be an easy thing.
What?! No...
Then I'm...
...If you are willing, you can live with us in these woods. Would you like that?
There are many Pixies here. They may not look like you, but they are your kind.
We can definitely support one more Pixie. It would please Titania as well.
Yes! You should stay with us!
You have nowhere to go right? It's settled then!
Err... Ummm... Yeah, I guess you're right.
I'll... Stay here. Thank you, Lord Oberon.
>The next day.

*Giggle*
Catch me if you can!
Just you wait! There! Gotcha!
C'mon, let's go to the flower field. Race you there!
(...I feel so lonely)
(Even though I promised to stay here, but still, I miss my friends back home.)
(This whole thing about another dimension and not being able to go back is just beyond me!)
There MUST be a way to get back home... And I'm gonna find it!

What the hell...
The whole world is trashed...!
There must be a clue on how to get back somewhere, there's gotta be!
There is no way I'm giving up...!

*Pant*
There must be... A way...
...I'm not sure there's anything to find in these mountains but...
*Sob*
Will I never see my friends again...? Ever?
Please... I just wanna go home...
To my friends...
>Pixie's wings fail her, and she drops to the ground...
Can't... move my wings. Can't... fly.
What's the use anyway... I'm never gonna find...
>With no strength left to keep her eyes open, Pixie loses consciousness.
>--Present day--
>Plagued by fever, Pixie mumbles feebly in her sleep...

*Pant*
Where are you... [sys user_name]...
>You feel a sharp pain coming from your abdomen.
>You were able to get your shield up right before impact, but part of the attack still got through.
>Wounded, you can feel your shirt soaking up the blood.
Alive... Still alive! Kill. Kill. Killlllll...!
>The unicorn is looking to finish you off.
>You can't afford to lose...!
